# =============================================================================
# Initial .gitignore for AtlasFishing Project (v0.1 foundation)
# =============================================================================
#
# This file defines the initial plan for files and directories that Git should
# ignore in the Atlas_Group3 repository. The goal is to keep the repository
# clean by excluding:
#   - Operating system artifacts
#   - Editor/IDE configuration (primarily VS Code)
#   - Node.js dependencies and build outputs (for future React or tooling)
#   - Temporary files, logs, and environment secrets
#
# This configuration is lightweight and suitable for a pure client-side web app
# using HTML, CSS, JavaScript. This is for our plan migrate to React.
# It follows patterns from GitHub's official Node.gitignore template.
#
# Last updated: Initial setup - February 24, 2026 - Berry
# =============================================================================

# -------------------------------
# Operating System generated files
# -------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini

# -------------------------------
# Editor and IDE files (VS Code primarily)
# -------------------------------
.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace

# -------------------------------
# Node.js / npm / package manager files
# -------------------------------
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json
.pnpm-debug.log*

# -------------------------------
# Build / distribution / output folders (future-proof for React or bundlers)
# -------------------------------
/dist/
/build/
/out/
/.tmp/
/coverage/

# -------------------------------
# Logs, temporary files, and caches
# -------------------------------
*.log
*.log.*
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
*~

# -------------------------------
# Environment / secrets (critical even if not yet used)
# -------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# -------------------------------
# Testing / coverage artifacts (For Later)
# -------------------------------
.nyc_output/
.lcov.info

# -------------------------------
# macOS-specific extended attributes
# -------------------------------
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
